SUMMARY:Building a Site with AI Tools: A Live Demo of ZipWP
DESCRIPTION:WordPress Lancaster\nThis month **Colby Weinhofer** will do a 
 real-time demo of building a site from scratch using the **ZipWP AI site b
 uilder**. This will be less presentation and more of an opportunity to see
  up close how user-friendly and capable an AI tool like this is. After see
 ing the tool in action\, the group will discuss the perceived strengths an
 d weaknesses of this approach for users (or clients) who don't need/want f
 ull custom development.\n\nPizza 🍕 and introductions at 7pm.\n\n🗒️
  About our location\n\nFree parking in lot off of market street. [See here
  for directions to The Candy Factory\, Warehouse D](https://goo.gl/maps/2N
 FNcZFxQC1qi8M66).
